[{"conversations": [{"content": "奇怪了。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "今天街上是不是特別安靜啊？完全看不到人……", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "嗯，不過可以感覺到窗戶另一邊有人的氣息。", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "你們是旅客嗎？", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "啥？不，我們不是旅客。你又是誰？", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我是喬，別人都稱我「手持爆炎弓的男人」。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "比起這個，勸你們也趕快躲起來比較好。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "躲起來？", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "隔壁鎮跑來的流氓，挾持了人質躲在餐廳裡面。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "你說什麼！？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "一開始只是在爭吵馬蹄濺起來的泥水到底有沒有弄髒披風。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "喂喂，那怎麼會演變成挾持人質事件？", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "因為對方是當地有權有勢的人。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "被逼到走投無路後，就抓人當人質，看能不能絕境逢生。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "抓人質就可以絕境逢生嗎……？不對，比起這個得趕緊去救人！", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "不急，先等等。他們也差不多該冷靜下來了吧。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "你的意思是冷靜後……會出來投降？", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "投降後被抓起來接受公正的審判？這個城鎮沒這麼正派啦。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "那些傢伙腦裡想的應該是「到底能拉幾個陪葬」吧。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "那就糟了……情況明明這麼危險，你在搞什麼？", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "就是因為情況危險啊。好了，看著吧。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "那些傢伙也差不多忍不住要出來了。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "可惡，居然敢玩弄我！", "speakerName": "流氓A", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "既然這樣就拿你來開刀，看我宰了你！", "speakerName": "流氓A", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "咿──！", "speakerName": "貴族", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "真的出來了！", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……哼。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "呀！", "speakerName": "流氓們", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "可惡，居然敢玩弄我！", "speakerName": "貴族", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "差不多就這樣吧。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "全、全部解決了！？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "好快啊……他射了箭嗎……？", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "喂，那邊的傢伙，你叫尤蒂爾吧？", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "咦？你知道我嗎？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "是啊，常聽到傳聞呢。處事挺高調的嘛。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "想跟你商量，有沒有興趣雇用我當保鑣？", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "保鑣嗎……如果能助我們一臂之力的話非常歡迎。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "不過你可要做好心理準備喔？", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我們跟其他騎士團截然不同，要面臨的可是地獄呢。", "speakerName": "蘭薩弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "好啊，我不介意。不對，應該是這樣正合我意。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "正合你意？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "是啊，地獄裡應該有令人膽顫心驚的刺激在等著我們吧？", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我啊，就是在尋找能賭上性命的勝負……", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}]}, {"conversations": [{"content": "喬，不好意思。城鎮附近發現了魔獸的巢穴，可以請你幫個忙嗎？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "魔獸啊……我正好想施展一下身手呢。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "殿下，請稍等。這個男人身手行嗎？", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "身手沒問題，上次親眼見識過了，我可以保證。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "要不然小姑娘也來確認一下？", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "居然叫我小姑娘……？這位先生講話真沒禮貌耶。", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "哎呀，這可失禮了。小姐，我並沒有惡意。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……哼。", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "尤蒂爾，可以佔用你一點時間嗎？", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "大概要多久？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "直到她相信我的身手為止。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "妳叫耶魯菲莉絲對吧？", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我會射中妳指定的樹，隨便妳選。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "那麼……雖然有點遠，就那根樹枝如何？", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "如果三支箭內能射中，我就認同你。", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "那根樹枝嗎……還真細啊。嗯，這……可能有點困難呢。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "哼……果然只是這點程度。看來根本沒必要確認。", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "總之我就試試看吧。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "那根樹枝……沒錯吧？", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "嗯，大概……", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "不過整棵樹都被轟飛了，也不知道到底有沒有射中。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "不，確實射中了喔，我對狙擊有自信。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "等、等一下等一下等一下！為什麼弓箭會把整棵樹連根轟走！？", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "而且箭看起來好像被火包圍著，那到底是……！？", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "沒什麼秘密。爆炎弓……那是我的得意招式。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "哈哈，好厲害的招式！", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "耶魯菲莉絲妳看，我說的沒錯吧？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "唔、嗯……身手確實是沒問題呢。", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我為懷疑你這件事致歉，喬。你是一流的射手。", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "妳能相信就好，這樣之後的工作也會比較好辦。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "好了，走吧，兩位。重頭戲才剛要開始呢。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}]}, {"conversations": [{"content": "喬。麵包烤好了喔。你不吃嗎？", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "嗯，聞味道就知道了。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "不過能讓我享受這個味道一會嗎？", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "當然沒關係……你喜歡烤麵包的味道嗎？", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "是啊，我的宿敵喜歡這味道。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "聞著這味道，我就會回憶起他的事情。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "回憶起他的事情……也就是說他已經不在這世上了？", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "是啊，在決鬥時，被我親手結束了性命。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "決鬥……？為了什麼決鬥？", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "在弓箭的世界裡，最強男人的稱號宛如遙不可及的頂峰。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我們是為了爭奪挑戰那地位的權利。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "為了這個理由就要決鬥！？男人真是令人無法理解啊。", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "是啊，我自己也不太懂。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "決鬥前的一個月裡，我跟他住在一起。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "什麼！？為什麼要跟未來會互相廝殺的人住在一起？", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "不知道，只能說我們對彼此有興趣吧。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "他是那種只看錢而不挑工作的人，也就是一般人說的大壞蛋。但在那一個月裡，我很幸福。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "幸福？明明對方是大壞蛋耶？", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "這樣不是每天都得面對死亡的緊張感嗎？", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "是啊，只要想背叛，隨時都可以背叛。不管是他還是我都一樣。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "但無盡的緊張最終變成了快感，我甚至開始覺得那男人很可愛。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "男人都是這樣子嗎！？", "speakerName": "耶魯菲莉絲", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "你們兩位還沒吃飯吧？先去吃吧。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "啊，不好意思，馬上就去。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}]}, {"conversations": [{"content": "喬，你在忙嗎？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "不，還好。不過你小心一點。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "因為弓箭的道具散落在地上。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "你在保養弓嗎？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "是啊，等一下陪我試射吧。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "試射是要怎麼試？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "把蘋果放在頭上，然後不要動就可以了。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "然後你射蘋果？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我不懂究竟為什麼要我把蘋果放在頭上。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "沒有啦，射箭就是要頭上放蘋果嘛！我也想試試弦的緊固程度。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "話說回來，尤蒂爾。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "如果我是來取你性命的殺手，你會怎麼辦？", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "如果你是殺手的話，應該馬上就會取我性命吧？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "而且我可沒那麼容易就被殺掉。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "是啊，但現在呢？", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "你應該沒想過我會殺你吧？", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "是沒錯。因為要是開始懷疑，可就沒完沒了。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "的確。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "好了，保養結束。試射時間到了。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我可不幫忙喔。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "別這樣啦，你應該稍微會用弓吧？", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "瞄準拉弓的話懂一點。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "那蘋果放我頭上，你負責把蘋果射下來。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我負責射！？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "沒問題，距離不會太遠，近到連新手也不太會射偏。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "問題不是這個吧！？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "而且，如果我因為剛才你說的話開始不信任你──", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "心裡懷疑「這傢伙或許是殺手，被殺之前先下手為強」，那你要怎麼辦？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "不知道，要試試看嗎？", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "怎麼可能試！　", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "你是重要的夥伴，我怎麼能射重要的夥伴……", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "喬，這就是你追求的刺激嗎？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我怎麼覺得你是一心求死？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "求死……的確也有人這麼說過。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "但這不是生或死的問題。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我目前為止已經跨過好幾次生死關頭。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "穿過箭雨，鑽過魔獸的腹部底下。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "那時候的刺激感讓我興奮不已。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "除此之外的時間，都讓我覺得無聊至極無法忍受。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "但是要是有個差錯，真的會死啊？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "雖然今天也活下來了，但明天不一定也會如此。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "就到時候再說吧，我不怕死。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……我怕死，我沒辦法像你那樣思考。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "為什麼要害怕？你自己不是也投入了賭命的戰場嗎？", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "你都這麼做了，為什麼怕死？", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "因為我還有想做的事。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "不能在這時候死去。所以，我一直都害怕戰場。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……！", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "你沒有夢想嗎？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "死前若沒有實現就會後悔的夢想。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "原來如此，夢想……夢想是嗎。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我早就遺忘了……", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}]}, {"conversations": [{"content": "咕嚕嚕嚕嚕嚕嚕……！", "speakerName": "魔獸", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "唔，太大意了……沒想到單獨行動時居然會遇到一大群魔獸。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "只能靠自己了，喝啊！", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "糟了，劍被咬住了……！？放、放開啊！", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "咕嚕嚕嚕嚕嚕嚕……！", "speakerName": "魔獸", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "劍、劍被彈開了！？再這樣下去……！", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "嘎喔喔喔喔！？", "speakerName": "魔獸", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "只憑一支箭……全滅……！？啊，爆炎弓！？……是喬嗎？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "喂，沒事吧！？", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "真是麻煩的王子，每次出門都會碰到危機。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "抱歉，終於得救了。我還以為死定了。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "喂喂，尤蒂爾，你不是怕死嗎？", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "既然怕死，為何不帶護衛出門。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "唔……沒辦法反駁，我太大意了。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "下次我會更珍惜自己的生命。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "不過，真不虧是喬啊。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "居然在一瞬間，就消滅了這麼多的魔獸……！", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……？喬，怎麼了？你的手在發抖……？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "……我很害怕。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "咦？", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我想到要是晚了一步，讓你死掉的話……放箭的手就開始發抖了。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我離開故鄉後就一直在旅行，所以已經忘了。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "忘了保護他人的恐怖……", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "喬……", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "也難怪孤獨的我，人生裡從不曾感受到刺激、嗎……", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "尤蒂爾……你說你有夢想對吧？", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "嗯，我要建立大家可以幸福生活的國家。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "讓耶魯菲莉絲、克菈兒、蘭薩弗……還有喬！大家都能幸福生活的國家！", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "呵呵，嘛，這樣也不錯呢……", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "我已經忘了夢想，現在仍想不起來。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "但就讓我試著守護你的夢想吧。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "比起沒有保護目標的戰場，這樣還比較……刺激。", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "怎麼樣？你願意用我這個亡命之徒嗎？", "speakerName": "喬", "type": "conversation"}, {"content": "嗯，當然！以後也請多指教啊，喬。", "speakerName": "尤蒂爾", "type": "conversation"}]}]